There is a statewide Youth Suicide Prevention School Program administered by the Department in cooperation with:
Participating local education agencies;
Local community agencies involved in suicide prevention;
Local community mental health programs; and
Youth service bureaus.

On or before October 1, 1986, the Department may establish a demonstration Youth Suicide Prevention School Program in cooperation with local education agencies in the following political subdivisions:
Anne Arundel County;
Baltimore City;
Baltimore County;
Harford County;
Howard County; and
Montgomery County.
